name: Christmas plum pudding studs
description:
Add some Christmas cheer to your ear!

These gorgeous little plum pudding stud earrings are handmade in Melbourne from polymer clay. Each one is approx. 1cm tall x 4mm depth.  Made with surgical steel posts and clasps so suitable for most sensitive ears. 
The earrings arrive beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon. A great accessory for any Christmas party, or cute teacher gift.

name: Christmas plum pudding earrings
description:
Add some Christmas cheer to your ear!

These gorgeous little plum puddings are handmade in Melbourne from polymer clay. Each one is approx. 1.2cm tall and they been made into a a fun pair of earrings. Studs are also available (see other listing)

The dangly earrings are made with sterling silver plated ear wires making them suitable for most sensitive ears.

The earrings arrive beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon. A great accessory for any Christmas party, or cute teacher gift.

name: Christmas plum pudding necklace
description:
Did you know that the tradition on plum pudding dates all the way back to Medieval times? Embrace the tradition with this super sweet little plum pudding necklace.
The tiny little pudding (approx. 1.2cm tall) is handmade from polymer clay and sits on a delicate ball chain necklace. 
The necklace sits short, resting on the collarbone. 
This item arrives beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon.
Please note it is a jewellery item, and not edible.

name: Miniature Gingerbread Necklace/Fairy Door accessory
description:
A super cute miniature gingerbread house, handmade from polymer clay and decorated with miniature lollies. 
Each house is approx. 2.5cm in size. 

Please choose either the necklace option (house comes with silver loop and ball chain necklace) or Fairy Door option (no loops, made as a single ornament).

Your little gingerbread house will arrive beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon.
Shipping a flat $5 rate within Australia, regardless of how many items you order.
Please note, as each house is handmade, the exact type and location of individual miniature lollies may vary slightly from the photo.

Although these little tiny houses look so realistic, they are not edible so please be careful around very small children.

name: Miniature Gingerbread House Xmas Tree Decoration
description:
An adorable little gingerbread house (approx. 2.5cm) which is beautifully decorated in miniature sweets. It comes with a ribbon to hang onto your Christmas tree. 

Handmade in Melbourne. Made from a lightweight clay so it won't weigh down the tree branch.

As each item is made by hand, the exact type and position of miniature lollies might vary slightly from the photo. This will be the cutest decoration on your tree!

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon. Please note-this item is not edible!

name: Saturday Lollipop Gift Voucher
description:
Do you know someone who would LOVE Saturday Lollipop jewellery, but just can't decide what to go for? How about a gift voucher so they can choose themselves. 

This voucher is for $33 which covers the cost of most items ($28) plus $5 postage within Australia. The voucher itself is mailed free of charge.  If you would prefer a voucher in a different amount, just send me a message and I will arrange it for you.

This voucher can be used on any item in the online shop, or even for a custom item. To order custom items, just send a message through this website. It is not redeemable for cash.

name: Licorice Allsorts or Jaffa Cupcake necklace
description:
Another adorable little cupcake necklace! This charm is just under 1.5cm tall. Choose from either the licorice allsorts necklace which features a pink base with rich brown cupcake, topped with a butter cream icing and teeny tiny little licorice allsorts. It looks so real, but it is 100% handmade from polymer clay.

The other option is a delicious looking Jaffa chocolate orange cupcake. A deep orange base, with chocolate icing, miniature jaffas and a slice of orange.

The charm comes on a silver plated ball chain necklace which sits short, close to the collarbone. If you prefer a longer chain just message me.

The necklace arrives beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, ready for giving.
This item can also be made into dangly earrings ($35). Just message me for this to be made.

name: Cookie Monster Cupcake Necklace
description:
This absolutely adorable miniature cookie monster necklace is approx. 1.5cm tall and handmade by me, from polymer clay. It comes on a silver tone ball chain necklace (46cm). Such a fun necklace, sure to make you smile.

This tem arrives beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making it the perfect gift for any cupcake/cookie fan or keen baker!

Remember, shipping cost is fixed at $5 within Australia no matter how many items you order, so feel free to add to your cart!

This item can also be made into dangly earrings ($35). Just message me to order this.

name: Waffle Studs
description:
Super scrumptious looking little waffles, handmade from clay and made into stud earrings. Choose from either Chocolate or Cream toppings. So delicious looking and very, very cute.

Made with surgical steel posts and clasps so suitable for most sensitive ears.

They come packaged in a gift box with ribbon, ready for giving. An ideal gift for a foodie friend.

name: Happy Little Vegemite Studs
description:
Are you a happy little Vegemite?

Gorgeous little vegemite jar earrings, handmade by me in Melbourne from polymer clay. These little jars are approx. 12mm tall, with surgical steel posts and clasps. 

These studs come beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making the perfect gift for a fan of Vegemite, or a fun present for a friend travelling overseas.

name: Nutella Studs
description:
Ahhh Nutella! Could you eat it straight from a jar with a spoon? I could!

Very cute miniature nutella jars, handmade by me in Melbourne from polymer clay. They are approx. 1cm tall and perfectly formed. With surgical steel posts and clasps these super fun earrings sure to bring a smile.

They come beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making the perfect gift for a chocoholic friend, or just to spoil yourself!

name: Delicious Baguette Sandwich necklace
description:
My new favourite! This super realistic little sandwich looks so fresh and tasty, you'll want to eat it up!  It is handmade using several different types of clay and hand painted. 

The sandwich is approx. 5-6cm long and sits of a delicate sterling silver chain. It is light weight and easy to wear. A very fun necklace which is sure to make you smile.

It arrives beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon.

Please note that as each sandwich is handmade, the exact size and positioning of the filling may vary slightly from one necklace to another. Although this looks particularly tasty, please do no try to eat it as it is 100% clay.

name: Cute Cupcake studs
description:
Gorgeous little cupcakes (approx. 12mm tall) made into adorable stud earrings.

This picture shows vanilla cupcakes in red sparkle cupcake bases, however any colour combo can be made. Please select from the options in the drop down box or email for special requests.

Surgical steel posts and clasps make these suitable for most sensitive ears.

The earrings arrive beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon and make a perfect present for someone who loves to bake.

options.name: Vanilla cake with red sparkle base & strawberry
Vanilla cake with pink base & flower
Chocolate cake with blue base & flower
Vanilla cake with choc frosting & heart, pink base

name: Chocolate Strawberry Studs
description:
Is there anyone out there who doesn't like chocolate coated strawberries? Nope, didn't think so!

These super sweet chocolate strawberry studs are handmade by me in Melbourne, using polymer clay.

Each strawberry is about 8mm tall and so scrumptious looking, you will wish it were edible! Made with surgical steel posts and clasps.

These earrings come beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, ready for giving, or just for treating yourself. Now you can have chocolate coated strawberries whenever you want!

name: Macaron Necklace
description:
The classic French macaron is back in vogue and so it should be! Such divine treats which not only taste amazing, but look so beautiful too! So beautiful in fact, wouldn't you just want to wear them?

This fun, colourful necklace with 6 miniature macarons made from polymer clay is sure to delight. Each macaron is perfectly handmade by myself, and sits on a delicate, silver tone ball chain necklace. The necklace is 43 cm and sits short, close to the collar bone.

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making the perfect gift for a foodie friend.

name: Chocolate Cupcake Necklace
description:
A very cute little 'chocolate' cupcake with icing and coloured sprinkles sits on this delicate silver tone ball chain necklace. The cupcake base can be made from different colours (select from the drop down box). The item photographed is with pale blue.

The cupcake is handmade by me in Melbourne, from polymer clay. The chain sits short (43cm) so rests on the collarbone.

This necklace is utterly scrumptious looking, but please don't try to eat it!

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making it the perfect gift for someone who loves baking cakes, or just a treat for yourself!

name: Nutella Necklace
description:
This miniature nutella jar is perfectly formed with great attention to detail. It is handmade from polymer clay and sits about 12mm tall.

The charm is presented on a delicate silver ball chain necklace with lobster clasp. The necklace is 43cm long.

A gorgeous little handmade necklace which would make a perfect gift for any nutella fans!

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, ready for giving.

name: Happy Little Vegemite Necklace
description:
A tiny, perfectly formed little vegemite jar sits on this delicate silver tone necklace.

The jar is made with incredible attention to detail, handsculpted from polymer clay. It sits about 12mm tall. The necklace rests on the collar bone (43cm) with a lobster clasp.

This fun little necklace is a great gift for anyone who adores their Vegemite, or as a souvenir for an international friend visiting Australia.

It come sbeautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon.

name: Cookie Jar Necklace
description:
Who stole the cookies from the cookie jar? Who me? Not me!

An adorable little glass jar (approx. 3.5cm tall) containing miniature 'choc chip' cookies made from clay. The jar sits on a long silver tone ball chian necklace (86cm) so the wearer can admire the cookies! The glass jar is super tough and strong enough to withstand all the usual bumps and clunks with no damage.

A fun necklace, sure to bring a smile. It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon making the perfect gift for a someone you love to share cookies with...or just for yourself!

name: Lollipop Jar Necklace
description:
Remember the thrill of going into an old fashioned lolly shop and looking up at all the sparkling glass jars filled with lollies? Bring back your childhood with this fun & unique necklace.

A super gorgeous little glass jar (3.5cm tall) containing tiny coloured lollipops, made from clay. The jar sits on a long (86cm) silver tone ball chain necklace. The chain is long enough that the wearer can admire the lollies! 
The lid is glued shut for safety and the super tough glass holds up to all the usual knocks without damage.

The necklace comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making an ideal gift for a special person, or just to treat yourself!

Please note, as each item is handmade, the exact colour of the lollipops may vary in each jar.

name: Teacup Necklace
description:
A nice hot cup of tea and a chat to one of your favourite people...one of life's simple pleasures!

This very cute blue & white porcelain tea cup and saucer is filled with 'tea' and a teeny tiny lemon slice, and sits on a delicate, silver tone ball chain necklace. The necklace chain is 43cm so sits close to the collar bone. An adorable little necklace, sure to make you smile.

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making the perfect gift for that person you love to catch up with over a cuppa.

name: Teacup Ring
description:
Who do you love to have a cuppa with?
An adorable silver plated adjustable ring featuring a tiny blue teacup with 'tea' and lemon. A very fun ring which is sure to make you smile. 
The teacup matches the teacup necklace (also available in this store) but is slightly small in size. 
It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making the perfect gift for someone you love to have a cuppa with!

name: Vegemite on Toast Brooch
description:
So simple, yet probably the best breakfast out there!

Hot, buttery toast with Vegemite, hmmmmmm, can't beat it!

This gorgeous little brooch is approx. 3cm in size and shows a tiny and amazingly realistic slice of toast with melting butter, miniature knife and jar of vegemite, resting on a red and white napkin.

Handmade from polymer clay, this adorable little brooch is guaranteed to make you smile.

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making it the perfect gift for an Aussie overseas needing a touch of home!

name: Loveheart Teacup necklace
description:
A nice hot cup of tea and a chat to one of your favourite people...one of life's simple pleasures!

This very cute blue & white porcelain tea cup and saucer is filled with 'tea' and a teeny tiny lemon slice, complete with a little biscuit on the saucer. It sits on a delicate, silver tone ball chain necklace. The necklace chain is 43cm so sits close to the collar bone. An adorable little necklace, sure to make you smile.

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, making the perfect gift for that person you love to catch up with over a cuppa.

name: Nutella Brooch
description:
It's a bit naughty, but as a treat I just adore warm, crispy croissants with lashing of gooey Nutella, yes please!!

This little brooch features just that! The little (3cm) plate holds a nutella jar and croissant, handcrafted from polymer clay, resting on a red and white napkin.

It comes beautifully packaged in a gift box with ribbon, ready for giving to a special person who loves all things chocolatey, or just as a calorie free treat for yourself!
